Class Arc

java.lang.Object
  Arc

public class Arc
extends java.lang.Object

COPYRIGHT (C) 2005 Rob Bauer. All Rights Reserved.

An object to represent an arc between two rooms. This object will behave (hopefully) as an edge of a graph.

Version:
1.0 2005-NOV-10
Author:
Rob Bauer
